{"tid":1651291,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"場仗未打完架","createTime":"2019-10-13T09:54:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T09:57:43.000Z","uid":266685,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b4404bca21aac87b6a0b2126a76ac4e72455951f","tid":1651291,"uid":266685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:54:11.000Z","msg":"美國人權民主法案未過、五大訴求未得到回應、手足繼續比人拉比人打、白色恐怖繼續漫延、死左既手足未沉冤得雪、黑警仲未清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咁撚多野未做 呢場仗仲有排打既時候 點解會係瘋狂互吊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地一齊行左咁耐 同路人有做得唔完美既地方咪拎出黎理性討論 跟住發揮自我改善功能再進化<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係一黎就即刻互吊 甚至威脅其他同路人 自我膨脹咁迫其他人聽你講 咁樣同成為大台 / 分化有咩分別</span></strong></span>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞返清楚目標 政權同佢班賤狗仲未被清算 仲未跪低架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要吊既人係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">港共、支那共匪、甘心做狗既香港警察仲有保皇黨班賤人</span></strong></span><br />\n呢班人先係我地目標 槍口要對準佢地而唔係自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家行得出黎就係為左守護我地既家 同我地應得既權利 我地各自爬山但目標係一致架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地一分化一割蓆就會輸架啦 輸左就真係乜都冇架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有野唔該以大局為重</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聚焦返十八區賽後檢討同黎緊既行動啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TPkmLw1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTPkmLw1.jpg&h=f930cec7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PY8C3iG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPY8C3iG.jpg&h=f179b8f8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/92cgzqo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F92cgzqo.jpg&h=1e401adb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3YLsLq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3YLsLq.jpg&h=dfd1604e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6dfe5339f0bfa1273dab22c3f3f5220f4ec0cd4","tid":1651291,"uid":266685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:55:22.000Z","msg":"搞清楚目標啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e88bef0fd148930258bc13900da9ba460de671","tid":1651291,"uid":266685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:55:35.000Z","msg":"搞清楚目標啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d302f2ec567ab78093d1d8a5eaebafc56e474b43","tid":1651291,"uid":266685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:55:54.000Z","msg":"搞清楚目標啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba99b1c1a1d97c1dfa2dbe07f5a9082f7f3e679e","tid":1651291,"uid":266685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:56:39.000Z","msg":"仲有好長既路要一齊行啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb0e090204de3dc724c82d9d010200d89c3f26f","tid":1651291,"uid":266685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:56:50.000Z","msg":"仲有好長既路要一齊行啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bceea8a1d93032505f6609ef10dd8526033da50","tid":1651291,"uid":266685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:57:13.000Z","msg":"仲有好長既路要一齊行啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8683e14e10f13fe6de58ded37fc0164197165206","tid":1651291,"uid":266685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:57:43.000Z","msg":"仲有好長既路要一齊行啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}